Laptop Magazine recently revealed its top gaming laptop brands for 2018, stating that MSI is now king of the castle. The publication ranked gaming laptop brands based on their score out of 100, which was calculated from six factors – design, display, innovation, software, warranty, and reviews. “The company pulled a serious power move and rose to the top spot thanks to laptops with stunning new designs, like the ultraslim GS65 Stealth Thin,” stated the report about MSI. “It doesn’t hurt that MSI has a massive library of gamer-centric software,” it added. The top 10 gaming laptop brands are listed in order below.